PROJECT: OpenCode SwiftBar Monitor
VERSION: 1.0.0
CREATED: 2024-12-26
LOCATION: ~/Projects/opencode-swiftbar-monitor

DESCRIPTION:
Real-time monitoring of OpenCode instances and Claude API usage 
directly from the macOS menu bar using SwiftBar.

MAIN COMPONENTS:
1. opencode-eventd - SSE listener daemon (real-time monitoring)
2. opencode-usaged - Usage statistics daemon (API tracking)
3. opencode.2s.sh - SwiftBar plugin (menu bar display)

QUICK START:
  cd ~/Projects/opencode-swiftbar-monitor
  bash install.sh

